org.mitre.mat.core
Class AttributeValueList

java.lang.Object
  org.mitre.mat.core.AttributeValueCollection
      org.mitre.mat.core.AttributeValueList

public class AttributeValueList
extends AttributeValueCollection

A (non-abstract) subclass of AttributeValueCollection for Lists intended to be used as an attribute value filler. This class almost implements List only not quite, because the add/set methods throw an AnnotationException if you try to add something invalid to the List. The class also tracks the attribute and document this collection is for.
